name: EduLivePro
tag_list: online, education, universty, secondaryeducation, softwaresolutions, onlineeducation
overview:
EduLivePro is a Online Education solution, offering a ready-made online university for educationists, with excellent features & major earning potential, in 24 hours!

EduLivePro offers a turnkey solution in the form of a ready-made university, which will be branded according to specifications of the traditional education provider and will enable the education provider to have online, fully-functional university within 24 hours. The online university software offers exciting features and benefits such as a comprehensive course content designed by an expert faculty, account areas for administration, faculty and students, negligible overhead costs—without any geographical barriers

EduLivePro has over 50 universities on its panel, which are providing online education through EduLivePro.
